{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/resources/bitcoin-nodes/","result":{"data":{"resourcesJson":{"page":"/resources/bitcoin-nodes/","title":"Bitcoin Nodes","lead":"Run your personal Bitcoin node.","description":"The Bitcoin network is a decentralized peer-to-peer (P2P) network made up of thousands of nodes. Each node keeps a copy of the Bitcoin blockchain and verifies every single transaction and block. By running a full node you can verify the state of the ledger yourself, rather than trusting a third party. Running a full node also makes the network more robust, making it more decentralized and resistant to certain types of attacks. Support the Bitcoin network by running your own full node.","body":null,"cardType":null,"lastUpdate":"30 June 2023","links":[{"title":"Start9","url":"https://start9.com/","description":"Personal server powered by StartOS, offering one-click installation and simple configuration of open source software services that run over Tor.","pills":[{"pill":"DIY","color":"green"},{"pill":"Plug & Play","color":"blue"}],"details":null,"image":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/d8a8f7c2f12e2ddc98066c933395ccbc/b8968/embassy.png","srcSet":"/static/d8a8f7c2f12e2ddc98066c933395ccbc/6fbd9/embassy.png 105w,\n/static/d8a8f7c2f12e2ddc98066c933395ccbc/88648/embassy.png 210w,\n/static/d8a8f7c2f12e2ddc98066c933395ccbc/b8968/embassy.png 420w,\n/static/d8a8f7c2f12e2ddc98066c933395ccbc/1a20b/embassy.png 840w","sizes":"(min-width: 420px) 420px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/d8a8f7c2f12e2ddc98066c933395ccbc/73ab7/embassy.webp 105w,\n/static/d8a8f7c2f12e2ddc98066c933395ccbc/b04e8/embassy.webp 210w,\n/static/d8a8f7c2f12e2ddc98066c933395ccbc/e1c45/embassy.webp 420w,\n/static/d8a8f7c2f12e2ddc98066c933395ccbc/cf69a/embassy.webp 840w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 420px) 420px, 100vw"}]},"width":420,"height":220}}}},{"title":"myNode","url":"https://mynodebtc